&gt; &gt; A mock object, easymock or otherwise, is a way of testing the 
&gt; &gt; _clients_ of an interface by substituting an alternative 
&gt; &gt; implementation. There are interesting trade-offs for the 
&gt; &gt; various techniques for implementing mock objects.
